Asus Vivobook S 14 OLED
I am highly impressed with the quality of this laptop: it is thin, offering decent battery life, extremely portable and highly useful device. 
I have decided to keep this as my business laptop, using it for learning, personal projects and all things professional. 
Of course, each device is slightly different in its own specifics, pros and cons, and I am currently having a great time learning more about this laptop, and learning about various topics of interest, while I am using this laptop. 
While using proprietary drivers and up to date Windows, as long as no serious modifications are made by the user, this laptop proves to be a pleasure to use daily. 
